OL,3,CRural school with no pupils to close
OL,4,Cfor good
OL,6,FA North Yorkshire primary school
OL,7,Fwithout a single pupil will
OL,8,Fpermanently close in less than a
OL,9,Ffortnight.
OL,11,FFountains Earth Church of England
OL,12,FPrimary School in Lofthouse, near ,
OL,13,Fwill officially shut on 31 March after
OL,14,Fthe local council approved its closure.
OL,16,FPupil numbers fell from 20 in 2017 to
OL,17,F10 in 2022 before parents, worried
OL,18,Fabout a lack of social interaction,
OL,19,Fpulled the remaining children out of
OL,20,Fthe school.
