OL,6,FAt a North Yorkshire Council meeting
OL,7,Fon 19 March in , Liberal Democrat
OL,8,Fcouncillor Andrew Murday put forward a
OL,9,Fplea to delay the closure and instead
OL,10,Finvestigate the federation responsible
OL,11,Ffor the school.
OL,13,FFountains Earth is part of Upper
OL,14,FNidderdale Federation alongside St
OL,15,FCuthbert's Church of England Primary
OL,16,FSchool in Pateley Bridge and
OL,17,FGlasshouses Community Primary School.
OL,19,FCllr Murday said: "Families have put
OL,20,Fhouses up for sale because the
OL,21,Fschool's not there.
