OL,6,F"It's a chicken and egg situation.
OL,7,FRural schools are important for
OL,8,Fcommunities and they gain something
OL,9,Ffrom being small and within the
OL,10,Fcommunity."
OL,12,FExecutive member for finance Cllr
OL,13,FGareth Dadd said keeping a school open
OL,14,Fwith such few potential pupils "would
OL,15,Fbe doing a disservice to those
OL,16,Fchildren."
OL,18,FThe council's legal officer Barry Khan
OL,19,Fsuggested it would be out of its remit
OL,20,Fto investigate governance at the
OL,21,Ffederation.
