OL,6,FOn conditions at the school leading up
OL,7,Fto its closure, Amanda Newbold,
OL,8,Fassistant director for education and
OL,9,Fskills at North Yorkshire Council,
OL,10,Fsaid: "Four to 11-year-olds were being
OL,11,Ftaught in one class.
OL,13,F"This was a challenge for the one
OL,14,Fmember of staff who then moved on and
OL,15,Fthe school struggled to recruit. They
OL,16,Frelied on agency staff or other
OL,17,Fteachers from the federation.
