OL,6,F"When a child became the only one in
OL,7,Ftheir year group, the parents wanted
OL,8,Fto move them to schools with other
OL,9,Fchildren their own age to prepare for
OL,10,Fsecondary school."
OL,12,FNorth Yorkshire Council's executive
OL,13,Fmember for education Annabel Wilkinson
OL,14,Fsaid "nobody wants to close a small
OL,15,Fschool" and called it "a very hard
OL,16,Fdecision."
OL,18,FThe school's catchment area will now
OL,19,Fbecome part of St Cuthbert's Church of
OL,20,FEngland Primary School in Pateley
OL,21,FBridge.
